Name: Frequency of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ following \First Look-Your updates are overdue\

Name: Percentage of manuscripts that reach \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ without \SW-Reviewer No Response\

Name: Number of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ preceded by \First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation\
Metric: Number of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' activities for cases where activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' occurs

Name: Percentage of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ out of all \Manuscript Export Succeeded\
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Frequency of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ in relation to \SW-EIC Accept\
Metric: Frequency of activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' for cases where activity 'SW-EIC Accept' occurs

Name: Percentage of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ that lead to \Manuscript Export Succeeded\
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Number of times \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ is performed per year
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'", 'aggregation': 'total', 'group_by': 'year'}

Name: Frequency of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ grouped by month
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'total', 'group_by': 'month'}

Name: Percentage of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ followed by \Manuscript Export Succeeded\
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Average number of days between \First Look-Your updates are due in one week\ and \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\
Metric: the average of the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'First Look-Your updates are due in one week'

Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Total \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ done by SYSTEM
Metric: Number of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' activities == 'SYSTEM' where ma is the last value of performer

Name: Ratio of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ over \SW-Reviewer Agreed\
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Occasions how often \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ is performed after \First Look-Please submit updates\
Metric: Number of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' activities for cases where activity 'First Look-Please submit updates' occurs
